comment: /**  * Returns the value for the given quantile based on the represented histogram statistics.  *  * @param quantile Quantile to calculate the value for  * @return Value for the given quantile  */
code: /**  * Returns the value for the given quantile based on the represented histogram statistics.  *  * @param quantile Quantile to calculate the value for  * @return Value for the given quantile  */ public abstract double getQuantile(double quantile).

comment: /**  * Returns the elements of the statistics' sample.  *  * @return Elements of the statistics' sample  */
code: /**  * Returns the elements of the statistics' sample.  *  * @return Elements of the statistics' sample  */ public abstract long[] getValues().

comment: /**  * Returns the size of the statistics' sample.  *  * @return Size of the statistics' sample  */
code: /**  * Returns the size of the statistics' sample.  *  * @return Size of the statistics' sample  */ public abstract int size().

comment: /**  * Returns the mean of the histogram values.  *  * @return Mean of the histogram values  */
code: /**  * Returns the mean of the histogram values.  *  * @return Mean of the histogram values  */ public abstract double getMean().

comment: /**  * Returns the standard deviation of the distribution reflected by the histogram statistics.  *  * @return Standard deviation of histogram distribution  */
code: /**  * Returns the standard deviation of the distribution reflected by the histogram statistics.  *  * @return Standard deviation of histogram distribution  */ public abstract double getStdDev().

comment: /**  * Returns the maximum value of the histogram.  *  * @return Maximum value of the histogram  */
code: /**  * Returns the maximum value of the histogram.  *  * @return Maximum value of the histogram  */ public abstract long getMax().

comment: /**  * Returns the minimum value of the histogram.  *  * @return Minimum value of the histogram  */
code: /**  * Returns the minimum value of the histogram.  *  * @return Minimum value of the histogram  */ public abstract long getMin().
